<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Toads Wild Adventure Support</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #071b2e;
      --card: #0f2d3f;
      --text: #f4fbf7;
      --muted: #b9d6cf;
      --accent: #77d66b;
      --accent-2: #f6d96b;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg), #0b3a3a);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    main {
      max-width: 860px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 40px 20px 64px;
    }

    header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 28px 18px;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.25rem);
      line-height: 1.1;
    }

    .subtitle {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin: 0 auto;
      max-width: 680px;
    }

    section {
      background: rgba(15, 45, 63, 0.86);
      border: 1px solid rgba(119, 214, 107, 0.28);
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 24px;
      margin: 18px 0;
      box-shadow: 0 14px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.22);
    }

    h2 {
      margin-top: 0;
      color: var(--accent-2);
      font-size: 1.35rem;
    }

    a {
      color: var(--accent);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    ul {
      padding-left: 1.25rem;
    }

    .contact {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      background: rgba(119, 214, 107, 0.12);
      border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
      padding: 14px 16px;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      margin-top: 28px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main>
    <header>
      <h1>Toads Wild Adventure Support</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Help Frog get home through a whimsical pond world of lily pads, turtles, owls, storks, fireflies, and Fly Feast challenges.</p>
    </header>

    <section>
      <h2>Contact Support</h2>
      <p class="contact">
        Need help, found a bug, or have feedback? Email support at:
        <br>
        <a href="mailto:salvatoreangelone@gmail.com">salvatoreangelone@gmail.com</a>
      </p>
      <p>Please include your device model, iOS/iPadOS version, and a short description of what happened.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>How to Play</h2>
      <p>The goal is to guide Frog safely back to the pond. Plan each move carefully, avoid hazards, and try to reach the pond in the best number of moves to earn more stars.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Owls can catch Frog.</li>
        <li>Storks fly across the board after a warning.</li>
        <li>Rocks block movement.</li>
        <li>Turtles and fireflies can help Frog.</li>
        <li>Fly Feast is a fast mini-game where Frog catches flies with a stretchy tongue.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Sound and Music</h2>
      <p>Sound and music can be toggled from the in-game controls. If you do not hear audio, check your device volume and Silent Mode settings.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Privacy</h2>
      <p>Toads Wild Adventure does not require an account, login, subscription, or purchase to play.</p>
      <p>The app does not collect personal information, does not include user-generated content, and does not include ads.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

      <h3>Do I need an internet connection?</h3>
      <p>No. Normal gameplay does not require an internet connection.</p>

      <h3>What is Grand Master mode?</h3>
      <p>Grand Master mode is a more challenging version of the pond puzzle game. It is designed to be harder while still remaining fair and solvable.</p>

      <h3>What is the Owl Immunity Pass?</h3>
      <p>The Owl Immunity Pass protects Frog from one owl catch in the main pond game. It can be earned through the Fly Feast mini-game.</p>

      <h3>How do streak rewards work?</h3>
      <p>Perfect 3-star levels build a streak. Reaching certain streak milestones unlocks special achievement illustrations.</p>
    </section>

    <footer>
      <p>&copy; 2026 Toads Wild Adventure. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
